#: xblock.py:64
msgid "Filters"
msgstr "Filtre"

#: xblock.py:66
msgid ""
"List of SQL filters to apply to the\n"
"               dashboard. E.g: [\"org='edX'\", \"country in ('us', 'co')\"]\n"
"               The fields used here must be available on every dataset used by the dashboard.\n"
"               "
msgstr ""
"Liste over SQL-filtre, der skal anvendes på dashboardet. F.eks.: [\"org='edX'\", \"country in ('us', 'co')\"]\n"
"               De anvendte felter skal være tilgængelige i hvert datasæt, der benyttes af dashboardet.\n"
"               "
